{"tid":511250,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得女朋友孝順係咪好事？","createTime":"2017-12-27T09:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T10:23:26.000Z","uid":136658,"like":57,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7beda40bb13d6dc388795a581738bd802ec952d5","tid":511250,"uid":136658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:49:57.000Z","msg":"一開始都好欣賞佢<br />\n但有時覺得佢over孝順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢都算有錢 老豆老母未到退休年齡已經唔洗做<br />\n一年去起碼3次旅行<br />\n總之佢一放假就會同屋企人去玩去嘆<br />\n<br />\n我想佢陪下我都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有幾次仲嗌交<br />\n問過佢愛情友情親情點排<br />\n佢 親情&gt;友情&gt;愛情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋晚又因為佢陪我陪得少而嗌左交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得女朋友咁應唔應該分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分手啦 人地唔啱你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你愛佢就應該比佢陪屋企人"},{"pid":"a6feddad8c033fc46c3352ab61bc364656281e96","tid":511250,"uid":41205,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:51:49.000Z","msg":"係你垃圾咋wor"},{"pid":"641e7f899923a5f220e81a42ed2cded9b136c442","tid":511250,"uid":57255,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:56:40.000Z","msg":"孝順到唔重視你就唔係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢連tum下你呃下你，話放你上第一位/同親人平排都唔肯，都唔慌有幾重視你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7081f6a6c6ed6e3a0b65f7d3b9adb50657899cda","tid":511250,"uid":136658,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係你垃圾咋wor</blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我應該有錢過佢 屋又大過佢<br />\n但我父母都仲未退休 話未到退休年齡都會繼續賺錢<br />\n但女友父母就一早退休嘆世界<br />\n朋友又返工<br />\n我都係想佢陪我多啲姐<br />\n之前啲女明明好痴身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460d0b01a511717138e04fe772a13dbf27f241cf","tid":511250,"uid":58140,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:57:49.000Z","msg":"你應該要癲過佢<br />\n佢有幾孝順 你勁佢幾倍<br />\n咁佢就會驚"},{"pid":"404ee0d8c83ae30f399f2219b0aa82adc9bfe7fb","tid":511250,"uid":136658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>孝順到唔重視你就唔係好事&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;<br />\n佢連tum下你呃下你，話放你上第一位/同親人平排都唔肯，都唔慌有幾重視你&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話對啲ex都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都唔知點 但佢口講又話好愛我"},{"pid":"317e35b8378e6558cebb9d97d1240593855ff9d5","tid":511250,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:00:07.000Z","msg":"呢啲好女仔 你唔要射比我"},{"pid":"2c0c5806217e1f8c94c7634f721d3ecd88f9a855","tid":511250,"uid":136658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:00:24.000Z","msg":"點解個個都正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fb268a52d160bb888f4a9d10f850ea7379c869","tid":511250,"uid":66122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:01:17.000Z","msg":"佢每年無同你去旅行咩？"},{"pid":"ae3918037a36550dd615d2be01c5bf10fa325b3d","tid":511250,"uid":136502,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:02:01.000Z","msg":"呢啲人先好 一結婚生埋bb<br />\n親情&gt;友情&gt;愛情<br />\n好似佢咁嘅觀念 <br />\n一組積家庭 你就排第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e954c69fd604b1ce994bcc8197fba5f86fd7260","tid":511250,"uid":136658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:04:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢每年無同你去旅行咩？</blockquote><br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢話屋企人唔比佢同異性去<br />\n但佢又會佢班好姊妹去<br />\n我叫佢呃老豆老母係同fd去都唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff8cbbde97c806bad1f3fb84511076560510028","tid":511250,"uid":136658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲人先好 一結婚生埋bb<br />\n親情&gt;友情&gt;愛情<br />\n好似佢咁嘅觀念 <br />\n一組積家庭 你就排第一&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n又好似幾有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想同佢組織家庭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf11fc99c6e7a9192e1770910c9f43fa04f857c","tid":511250,"uid":50253,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"有時你要諗下  係咪你放愛情第一先OVER左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企人陪佢成長左咁多年<br />\n佢覺得佢地最重要係合情合理"},{"pid":"efce84d1e8856e61c9db90f4e6c6f7010da5f7ae","tid":511250,"uid":43436,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"我覺得親情&gt;友情&gt;愛情 冇乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ne d女仔先娶得過"},{"pid":"d5f3bc3816536907982bf19a24e7691fbf56fbae","tid":511250,"uid":136658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:09:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時你要諗下  係咪你放愛情第一先OVER左&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/wink.png&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt; <br />\n屋企人陪佢成長左咁多年<br />\n佢覺得佢地最重要係合情合理</blockquote><br />\n我一開始都會咁諗架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢真係乜都屋企又先 有時想啲節日正日同佢一齊 佢就永遠留個翌日比我"},{"pid":"c6fc474ff9af9aacb07e2e3bec46f1f1c2eccedf","tid":511250,"uid":57255,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"efce84d1e8856e61c9db90f4e6c6f7010da5f7ae","tid":511250,"uid":43436,"like":3,"dislike":1,"s